- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper discusses modifications to Cartesian Genetic Programming, which is a type of evolutionary algorithm used in neural network design. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses a new form of genetic programming that can be used for machine learning tasks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses a new form of genetic programming that can be used for artificial intelligence tasks. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses a new form of genetic programming that can be used for system design and control tasks.
